  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2003-09-05",
    "date": "2003-10-10T13:26:04Z",
    "text": "Amends the Soldiers' and Sailors' Civil Relief Act of 1940 to allow a lessee to terminate a residential or motor vehicle lease which was entered into before military service or before receiving permanent change of station or deployment orders at any time after: (1) entry into military service; or (2) the date of the lessee's station or deployment orders. (Currently, a lessee may terminate only a residential lease and only after entry into military service.)"
  },
